examined the list and earlier determined that 39 prisoners had 
committed atrocious crimes against the nicaraguan people and 
had not demonstrated will to change their ways 
but during tuesdays debate opposition representatives noted 
that the organization of american states interamerican commission 
on human rights had recommended that the leftist sandinista 
