trade agreement which took effect jan 1 calls for the gradual 
phaseout of all tariff barriers and most nontariff barriers 
between the two countries over the next 10 years 
while the trade pact spelled out the cuts to be made each year in 
tariffs on particular products it provided for an acceleration if 
